	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The Master System can display more colors per tile than NES, but not quite as many as Genesis. You might have better luck trying to emulate 8-bit Sonic. Hang on a moment while I try to see how well the gradient that I made <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?p=124228#p124228" class="postlink">here</a> might work.<br /><br />Dithering out the &quot;dark green&quot; color let me cut it down to three palettes: sky and top of grass, grass and top of dirt, and solid dirt. This should allow drawing slopes with the grass and top of dirt palette as a transition.

		
